summary: A help guide for tracelog errors. TXT file for notepad. Virusproof.
descriptionHtml:
A help guide for tracelog errors. Download, open with notepad or whatever, read it and fix your NMM crash on your own.

All of my guides are written in notepad and are text documents. Virus proof unless you already have one running around your system.

THIS IS NOT A MOD. DO NOT TRY TO INSTALL IT WITH NMM.

NOTE:  This is ONLY for NMM related mod crashes.  I have NO way to write a log concerning BOSS crashes.
author: Thorne67
